flowchart TD
    A[Start: validated findings and recommendations] --> B[Define audience and key decision]
    B --> C[Craft headline answer in one sentence]
    C --> D[Select strongest 2 to 4 evidence points]
    D --> E[Build report.html with charts and context]
    E --> F[Create concise print-ready summary layout]
    F --> G[Render true summary.pdf via headless browser]
    G --> H[Add caveats and clear next actions]
    H --> I[Include appendix and methodology in HTML]
    I --> J[Package report.html, summary.pdf, notebook.ipynb]
    J --> K[Update learning files]
    K --> L[Final delivery checkpoint]
